## Python
```Python
from math import isqrt
def A055064(n): return ((m:=1<<n)<<n)+((s:=isqrt(m))**2*(s+1)-sum((q:=m//k)*((k<<1)+q+1) for k in range(1,s+1))>>1) # _Chai Wah Wu_, Oct 22 2023
```
